    <string name="dialog_prerelease_desc_message">• <b>Alpha Channel</b>: Early development stage. Low stability, may contain severe bugs. Includes experimental features and potential breaking changes.\n\n• <b>Beta Channel</b>: Feature-complete stage. No major new features or breaking changes. Focuses on UI/UX refinements and minor adjustments.\n\n• <b>Pre Channel</b>: Highly stable. No further functional changes. Dedicated to stability improvements and performance tuning for the final release.\n\n• <b>Canary Channel</b>: Rolling release automatically built by CI. Includes the absolute latest commits. May be unstable but offers the fastest access to new features.</string>
    
